These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pear, strawberry
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, bike
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person eating pear is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | pear   | strawberry   |
| Transport   | bike | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, climbing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | water | lemonade   |
| Sport      | climbing | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, tomato
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, reggae
1. the person eating pumpkin is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | tomato | pumpkin |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | reggae     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
