2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the person eating kiwi##8
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Food   | carrot | kiwi |
| Pet    | guinea-pig    | mouse |

